name: Klaipeda - Deive
tagline: Unofficial reference to the upcoming Tree of Savior MMORPG by imcGAMES
body:
### Klaipeda.xyz
This site is a planned fansite for the upcoming [Tree of Savior] (http://TreeOfSavior.com) game. Klaipeda is one of the 3 cities in the game, it's also the name of one of the largest city in Lithuania.

### Project Delve
Project Delve (which means "Goddess" in Lithuanian) is an upcoming iOS Reference app for the game. 

### Authors and Contributors
This project is currently authored by @GXLye.
